apps

Legume-service (port 8080) can create vegetables and send messages to hero-service (port 8081) to create superheroes

Usefull commands:

```yml
curl -v -L http://localhost:8080/health/live
curl -v -L http://localhost:8081/health/live

curl -v -L http://localhost:8080/health/ready
curl -v -L http://localhost:8081/health/ready

curl -v http://localhost:8080/q/metrics
curl -v http://localhost:8081/q/metrics


curl -v -XPOST  http://localhost:8080/legumes/init
curl -v http://localhost:8080/legumes
curl -v http://localhost:8081/heroes
```
